  "prompt": "If I were to watch my last movie, which movie would you recommend?",
  "response": "If you're looking for a movie that could leave a lasting impression, I'd recommend something that has strong emotional resonance, thought-provoking themes, and transcendent beauty. One such movie is \"The Shawshank Redemption.\" \n\n\"The Shawshank Redemption\" is a story of hope, friendship, and redemption, set against the backdrop of a life sentence in prison. It's a powerful and moving film that beautifully captures the resilience of the human spirit. The performances, writing, and cinematography make it a timeless classic. Watching this film can provide a deeply satisfying and memorable experience for your final movie viewing.",
